</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Michael McDonald w=
ent to El Salvador and tried to pay for goods and services in the country=
=E2=80=99s legal tender, Bitcoin. It went about <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
